details.name: Reincarnation
details.description: Wraith King's form regroups after death, allowing him to resurrect when killed in battle.  Upon death, enemy units in a 900 radius will be slowed. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: If a nearby allied hero is slain, they will be transformed into a wraith and have their death delayed for 7 seconds.
